comments.body:
Thanks for reaching out.

The `docker` transport does not support `tag@digest` and I do not know of plans to support it.  The reason to support it in the tools was to remain compatible with Docker by popular request.  Using the explicit transports notation of containers/image is leaving the Docker space.

 @mtrmac do you have a link to the issue where you elaborated on the decision to not support tag@digest in c/image?
